MIME-Version: 1.0

Bitcoin has come a long way from where it started. What began as something =
you could run and verify yourself has slowly turned into something most peo=
ple only access through apps and platforms. Along the way, many have lost t=
he ability to fully experience Bitcoin the way it was originally designed.

Today, Nakamoto is bringing that experience back.

The Nakamoto Desktop App is a new way to interact with Bitcoin directly fro=
m your computer. It gives you the ability to mine Bitcoin using your own ma=
chine, run your own node to verify the network, and see exactly where your =
Bitcoin lives on-chain. Everything happens under your control, without rely=
ing on third parties or hidden systems.

Beyond that, the app introduces tools that many holders have been waiting f=
or. You can secure your Bitcoin using deep cold storage with built-in time =
locks, and set up inheritance rules so your Bitcoin can be passed on safely=
 in the future without exposing your keys. It is designed not just for toda=
y, but for long-term ownership and peace of mind.

This is not about trading or speculation. It is about experiencing Bitcoin =
in a more complete and meaningful way. Whether you have held Bitcoin for ye=
ars or are just getting started, this gives you a way to move from simply o=
wning Bitcoin to truly understanding and controlling it.

If you have ever wanted to experience Bitcoin beyond just a balance on a sc=
reen, this is your opportunity.


		Explore the Nakamoto Desktop App and download it for your system. Downloa=
d the Nakamoto Desktop App here: https://www.nakamotodesktop.app/


Take a moment to see what Bitcoin feels like when it is fully in your hands=
.

Best regards,
The Nakamoto Team
